task_description: In app markor, Task-Oriented: Change the URL in the address bar to 'www.google.com' and navigate to the Google homepage.
In app markor, Browse the 'More' menu to find the current version of the Markor app, which is 'Version v2.10.9 (146)'.
In app markor, Remove the 'Forgotten Password | Can't Log In | Fa... m.facebook.com' entry from the history.
In app markor, Task-Oriented: Navigate to the 'Documents' folder, create a new text file named 'MeetingNotes.txt', and then add the text 'Meeting with John at 2 PM' to the file.
In app markor, Task-Oriented: Navigate to the 'Internal storage' and then create a new text file named 'MyNewFile.txt' in the 'Documents' folder.
In app markor, Open the browser settings by clicking the three-dot menu and then selecting 'Settings'.
In app markor, Task-Oriented: Allow Google Lens to access photos, videos, music, and audio on this device by clicking 'Allow' in the permission dialog.

In app markor, Identify the plant in the image by clicking on the 'Identify plants' option. If the identification fails, click 'Try again' to retry. If it continues to fail, return to the previous screen.
